    "\n",
    "> The most powerful stealth tool — patches ChromeDriver to bypass bot detection  \n",
    "> Works on sites like Cloudflare-protected pages  \n",
    "\n",
    "```bash\n",
    "pip install undetected-chromedriver\n",
    "```"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
