    "---\n",
    "## Selenium vs Scrapy — When to use which?\n",
    "\n",
    "| Feature | Selenium | Scrapy |\n",
    "|---------|----------|--------|\n",
    "| JavaScript pages | ✅ Yes | ❌ No (use Splash/Playwright) |\n",
    "| Speed | 🐌 Slow (real browser) | ⚡ Fast (async HTTP) |\n",
    "| Login/interaction | ✅ Easy | 🔧 Manual cookie handling |\n",
    "| Large scale (1000+ pages) | ❌ Heavy | ✅ Built for this |\n",
    "| Built-in pipeline | ❌ Manual | ✅ Items + Pipelines |\n",
    "| Beginner-friendly | ✅ Yes | 🔧 Moderate |\n",
    "\n",
    "**Rule of thumb:** Use Selenium when JS/login is needed. Use Scrapy for large-scale static page scraping."
   ]
  },
